        <li>bnf_art1->Fragments overlap like [bnf_poetic_image], then settle into a slow pattern.</li>
        <li>bnf_art1->Themes rise, [bnf_motion_verb] against [bnf_space] until they dissolve.</li>

        <li>bnf_art2->A figure returns again and again, [bnf_motion_verb] at the edge of silence.</li>
        <li>bnf_art2->Between takes, you can almost hear [bnf_scene_detail].</li>
